Tidjani Amadou Moutari Kalala (amụrụ ya na 19 Jenụwarị 1994) bụ onye Nijeiria ọkachamara na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba n'etiti maka otu egwuregwu Turkish Tuzlasporlisten (help·info)
A mụrụ ya na Arlit, Moutari nọrọ ọrụ mbụ ya na Niger na France ma na-agbara Akokana na Le Mans B.
Na Jenụwarị 2014, Moutari bịnyere aka na Metalurh Donetsk na Ukrainian Premier League, si otú a bụrụ onye Nijeria mbụ na-agba na league ahụ.
N'ọnwa Julaị, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta afọ anọ na otu egwuregwu Russia Anzhi Makhachkala.
Na 25 Jenụwarị 2017, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta ya na klọb Hungary Ferencváros.
Na 13 Febụwarị 2019, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta ya na klọb Hungary Mezőkövesd.
Na 29 Mee, Moutari bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta na otu egwuregwu nke Hungary Budapest Honvéd.
Na 10 Ọktoba 2020, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta ya na klọb Saudi Al-Ain.
Na 31 Ọgọstụ 2021, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta afọ abụọ na klọb Saudi Al-Fayha.
Na 31 Ọgọstụ 2022, Moutari bịnyere aka na nkwekọrịta ya na otu egwuregwu nke Saudi Al-Qadsiah. Na 31 Jenụwarị 2023, Al-Qadsiah tọhapụrụ Moutari.
O mere nke mbụ ya na mba Niger n'afọ 2012, mgbe ọ na-asọmpi n'afọ 2012 Africa Cup of Nations gbajiri ụkwụ ya n'egwuregwu ya na Gabon.
